*												*
*				Car Rental Management Application				*
*					     Manual						*
*												*
*************************************************************************************************
	
DESCRIPTION
		This application helps car rental management work to be more convenient. It does 
		supply basic features (packed as commands) for database viewing, appending.
	
USAGE
		Here are the list of commands (type 'man <command>' for more details) that can be
		used to interact:
		
			* 'view': 	Viewing database by 2 modes: view all / at a specific
					position.
			* 'delete':	Deleting the whole database or specific record.
			* 'add':	Adding new record into database.
			* 'edit':	Edit data at specific record in database.
			* 'rent':	Adding rental data for a specific record.
			* 'search':	Search information trough the database.
			* 'exit':	Exiting the program.
	
INSTALLATION
		This application requires Java SDK (se 1.7+) to be installed.
		For Windows it is provided at:
			http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/index.html
		For Ubuntu:
			#sudo apt-get install python-software-properties
			#sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/java
			#sudo apt-get update
			#sudo apt-get install oracle-java6-installer
		Uni-Platform (within terminal or command prompt):
			#java AppMain
	
